text: Shin Goo (; born Shin Soon-ki, ; August 13, 1936) is a South Korean actor. In 2010, he was awarded the 2011 Bogwan Order of Cultural Merit (South Korea) by the government. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean movie actors Category:South Korean stage actors Category:South Korean television actors
